msgid "Brewing Stand"
msgstr "Edabeetarako euskarria"

msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "Inbentarioa"

msgid "To use a brewing stand, rightclick it."
msgstr "Edabeetarako euskarri bat erabiltzeko, egin eskuin-klik."

msgid "To brew, you need blaze powder as fuel, a brewing material and at least 1 glass bottle filled with a liquid."
msgstr "Edabeak egiteko, erregai gisa blaze-hautsa, elaborazio-material bat eta likido batez betetako kristalezko botila bat behar dituzu."

msgid "Place the blaze powder in the left slot, the brewing material in the middle slot and 1-3 bottles in the remaining slots."
msgstr "Jarri blaze-hautsa ezkerreko hutsunean, elaborazio-materiala erdiko hutsunean eta 1-3 botila gainerako hutsuneetan."

msgid "When you have found a good combination, the brewing will commence automatically and steam starts to appear, using up the fuel and brewing material. The potions will soon be ready."
msgstr "Konbinazio on bat aurkitzen duzunean, elaborazioa automatikoki hasiko da eta lurruna agertzen hasiko da, erregaia eta elaborazio-materiala erabiliz. Edabeak prest egongo dira laster."

msgid "Different combinations of brewing materials and liquids will give different results. Try to experiment!"
msgstr "Elaborazio-materialen eta likidoen konbinazio desberdinek emaitza desberdinak emango dituzte. Saiatu esperimentatzen!"

msgid "Brew Potions"
msgstr "Edabeak prestatzea"

msgid "The stand allows you to brew potions!"
msgstr "Edabeen euskarriak edabeak egiteko aukera ematen dizu!"

